0.1.name: wordpress/woocommerce-my-account-widget
0.1.description:
The WooCommerce My Account Widget allows shop managers to display customer information in a widget.

Features

  • Display link to shopping cart
  • Display number of items in shopping cart
  • Display number of unpaid orders
  • Display number of uncompleted orders
  • Display number of files left to upload (working with our WooCommerce Upload My File plugin
  • Display a log-in form when logged out
  • Localisation: English & Dutch

** WooCommerce Upload My File plugin ** This widgets shows also the number of files the customer has to upload, when you use our WooCommerce Upload My File plugin. More information about that plugin on our website.
